      "votes_up": 0,
      "playtime_at_review": 3014,
      "review_text": "!!YOU CAN STILL PLAY PRE 1.0 GAME SETTINGS->PROPERTIES->BETAS->LEGACY!!\n\nGame as of 1.0 is not it. It now lags (fps drops/stutters) if you spam a bunch of coins onto the pusher or have ton of coins on the pusher, coins dont even push themselves anymore and they morph inside each other, theres also fps/game world skips if you are in super vsync mode (only happened while looking 1 direction inside the mall). The coin pushers also only have a small window for coins to actually be pushed, and it  seems like they cant move until the pusher is almost at the end. So no more random drops. Not sure what happened while rebuilding but it definitely needs some more tuning. Hopefully this isnt the last update. Definitely putting a recommendation back once the game is put back to its former performing state.",
